| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2540 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 316a9522-f83d-5c2e-a0ff-096cf6264af6"
